'''查方言'''（{{lang-hr|čakavski}}<ref>{{cite web|title=Hrvatski jezični portal (1)|url=http://hjp.novi-liber.hr/index.php?show=search_by_id&id=f1tiURA%3D&keyword=%C4%8Dakavski|accessdate=21 March 2015|archive-date=2020-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200529234543/http://hjp.novi-liber.hr/index.php?show=search_by_id&id=f1tiURA%3D&keyword=%C4%8Dakavski|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是[[克羅埃西亞語|克羅埃西亞語]]的三大方言之一，主要分佈在克羅埃西亞的沿海地區。查方言和[[什托方言|什托方言]]的互通度很低<ref name=Slavicintell>{{Cite web |url=http://www.academia.edu/4080349/Mutual_Intelligibility_of_Languages_in_the_Slavic_Family |title=Mutual intelligibility of languages in the Slavic family |access-date=2016-01-02 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011158/https://www.academia.edu/4080349/Mutual_Intelligibility_of_Languages_in_the_Slavic_Family |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且查方言的內部也有很大差異。查方言也是克羅埃西亞語文學最早的標準語言。

